☐ TEST_MODE = false
☐ Database credentials changed from examples
☐ API_TOKEN_SECRET is a long random string (min 32 chars)
☐ All API_CORS_ORIGINS are your actual domains
☐ HTTPS is enabled (API_REQUIRE_HTTPS = true)
☐ .env file is NOT committed to version control
☐ .env is added to .gitignore
☐ Only .env.example is in version control
☐ File permissions: chmod 600 .env (readable only by owner)
☐ ERP credentials use OAuth tokens, not hardcoded passwords
☐ Cloud storage keys are from IAM users with minimal permissions
☐ Logging is enabled for troubleshooting
☐ Monitoring/alerts are configured
☐ Backup system is tested and working
☐ Database has been backed up before deployment
☐ SSL certificate is valid and not self-signed (unless internal)
*/

